    "date": "2019-03-26T14:44:44Z",
    "text": "Everyday Philanthropist Act \n\nThis bill allows employers to offer certain employees a tax-advantaged flexible giving account as a fringe benefit. Flexible giving accounts allow employees to set aside up to $5,000 of their annual pretax earnings to make tax-deductible charitable contributions without having to itemize tax deductions."
